data.description:
Welcome to this charming single-story 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in this quiet Brooklyn Park neighborhood. This property features new carpet in the basement with a non-egress bonus room. A brand-new roof installed in July 2023, new windows installed in 2019, water heater less than a year old, and new sewer lines. The bonus room above the oversized, heated garage adds versatility to the property, serving as a potential office or keep for extra storage. Sitting on an oversized lot, the property offers ample outdoor space for gardening, play, or future expansion. With these upgrades and unique features, it's a comfortable and attractive place to call home. Only minutes from the Mississippi River Park and Trails, with easy access to 252/94/610/169.
Motivated seller make an offer today!
